Suggested-by: Peter Zijlstra <peterz@infradead.org>
Tested-by: Manali Shukla <Manali.Shukla@amd.com>
Tested-by: Brendan Jackman <jackmanb@google.com>
Tested-by: Michael Kelley <mhklinux@outlook.com>
