option is not set allows the compiler to omit unnecessary code.

Signed-off-by: Rik van Riel <riel@surriel.com>
Tested-by: Manali Shukla <Manali.Shukla@amd.com>
Tested-by: Brendan Jackman <jackmanb@google.com>
